  "detailed_description": "<strong>Miracle Heroes</strong> is a multiplayer light rogue-like game where players must select suitable combinations from a rich arsenal of weapons and items to enhance their gear and survive in a world fraught with danger.<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 heroes with unique appearances and completely different gameplay.<br></li><li>Hundreds of weapons, each with its own characteristics. Upgrade your weapons and combine two top-tier weapons to create new legendary artifacts.<br></li><li>Over 200 items with diverse combinations and various special effects.<br></li><li>A customizable equipment system for personalized adjustments.<br></li><li>A variety of maps and difficulty levels offering different challenges.<br></li><li>Unlike other survival games, in this game, you can jump and have access to the Z-axis space.<br></li><li>With Workshop support, we will open 70% of the game's content, significantly enhancing creative freedom.<br></li><li>Supports local multiplayer and online multiplayer.(Supports up to three players online)(Local multiplayer requires at least two controllers connected.)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/a876923da76a881f4cd4872828ea11ac.poster.avif?t=1757553385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/a876923da76a881f4cd4872828ea11ac.webm?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.poster.avif?t=1757553385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.webm?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.mp4?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Miracle Heroes</strong> is a multiplayer light rogue-like game where players must select suitable combinations from a rich arsenal of weapons and items to enhance their gear and survive in a world fraught with danger.<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 heroes with unique appearances and completely different gameplay.<br></li><li>Hundreds of weapons, each with its own characteristics. Upgrade your weapons and combine two top-tier weapons to create new legendary artifacts.<br></li><li>Over 200 items with diverse combinations and various special effects.<br></li><li>A customizable equipment system for personalized adjustments.<br></li><li>A variety of maps and difficulty levels offering different challenges.<br></li><li>Unlike other survival games, in this game, you can jump and have access to the Z-axis space.<br></li><li>With Workshop support, we will open 70% of the game's content, significantly enhancing creative freedom.<br></li><li>Supports local multiplayer and online multiplayer.(Supports up to three players online)(Local multiplayer requires at least two controllers connected.)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/a876923da76a881f4cd4872828ea11ac.poster.avif?t=1757553385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/a876923da76a881f4cd4872828ea11ac.webm?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.poster.avif?t=1757553385\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.webm?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095600/extras/b46cf953238d9eb458468e1a5b1412ff.mp4?t=1757553385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
